chunks.text:
In this Act the following words and expressions are used in the following
senses, unless a different intention appears from the context --
business includes any trade, occupation, or profession;
court includes every court and judge having jurisdiction in the case;
incorporated limited partnership has the meaning given in the Limited
Partnerships Act 2016 section 3;
land includes hereditaments, corporeal and incorporeal, of any tenure;
limited partnership has the meaning given in the Limited Partnerships Act 2016
Section 3; person includes any body of persons corporate or unincorporated; writing includes print, and written includes printed.
